  "instructions": [
    {
      "id": "e0b9c85e-fdc2-42f0-8830-e25d93f62a4c",
      "url": null,
      "text": "Z 5 bielkov vyšľaháme sneh, múku a cukor preosejeme. Do snehu najprv vmiešame cukor, potom múku a nakoniec orechy.",
      "image_url": null,
      "sort_order": 0,
      "is_group_header": false
    },
    {
      "id": "7db45874-dcfd-475a-b79e-a2e13199cbb0",
      "url": null,
      "text": "Vylejeme do vymastenej formy a dáme do dobre vyhriatej trúby na 180°C na minimálne 3/4 hodiny. Vrch sa nám môže trochu pri pečení dvihnúť. Po upečení ešte horúce aj s formou zabalíme do alobalu a necháme stáť do ďalšieho dňa, aby orechy zvlhli a dali sa pekne krájať.",
      "image_url": null,
      "sort_order": 1,
      "is_group_header": false
    },
    {
      "id": "88ee5fee-721c-4eae-93f5-a60dfa1a6ab8",
      "url": null,
      "text": "Po odstátí nakrájame ostrým nožom na tenké plátky (3,5 mm). Porozkladáme ich na plech a necháme sušiť v rúre na 100-150°C na teplovzdušnom režime (5-15 min). Keksíky takto pekne stvrdnú a zružovejú.",
      "image_url": null,
      "sort_order": 2,
      "is_group_header": false
    }
  ],
